{"id": 3104, "genre": 1001, "title": "这些年通过社交网络，你对「孤独」有了哪些新的理解？", "description": "社交网络杀死孤独，也生出些新的孤独。（题图来自：iStock ©️ jossdim ）", "record_count": 1339, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20191226190102WXJwyjnKbgTYQiZM.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2019-12-26T17:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 351234, "content": "通过社交网络结识一些人，因为社交网络淡忘更多人。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1671346}, {"id": 351750, "content": "我可能拥有享受孤独的突变基因，可是它很可能导致我无后，这是个矛盾。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 775953}, {"id": 351243, "content": "交流的对象被关在了这个玻璃盒里so sad", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1455600}, {"id": 351500, "content": "你有了可以不反馈的理由。面对面就不一样了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1676455}, {"id": 351245, "content": "像是活在现实和网络的夹缝里，无论哪边比起归属感体会到更多的差异感。想发动态，在备忘录里打打删删最后就只存在了备忘录里，因为发出去也没人交流，打完字就相当于发完了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1275438}, {"id": 351506, "content": "明明身边很多人，却没有一个人可以说话……工作生活的压力，两点一线，随时可因为小事各种崩溃……", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1676465}, {"id": 352530, "content": "每天下意识性地点开几个特点的App。如果不做，感觉自己被世界抛弃了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1670972}, {"id": 351259, "content": "相聚后的离别", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1675976}, {"id": 351261, "content": "现实中孤独，虚拟里侃侃而谈", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1674816}, {"id": 352542, "content": "网抑云没10级都不敢说自己有抑郁症", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1689019}, {"id": 351264, "content": "什么都喜欢一个人，喜欢独处。孤独其实也是一种生活态度啦~", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1676010}, {"id": 351265, "content": "聊天恐惧症", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1554064}, {"id": 351270, "content": "看着微信联系人，发现经常联系的没几个", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1020584}, {"id": 351272, "content": "现实中无人可聊，网络中无人可谈。抱着手机就是，，，，烦躁烦躁又烦躁，然后突然刷起视频看起小说，一天就过去了", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1142153}, {"id": 352298, "content": "只敢在不认识自己的群里胡闹", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1680135}, {"id": 351540, "content": "自己，是从生到死唯一的伴侣", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1666326}, {"id": 351801, "content": "并不孤独，网络世界网友很多，网络是用来缩短距离的，只是你失去了耐心，孤独都是自己造成的。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1450754}, {"id": 351295, "content": "晚上失眠的时候突然想找个人聊一聊 翻了很久不知道找谁 好不容易决定了谁 却又开始预想的对话 害怕自我剧透完全正确瞬间又失去了聊天的想法", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 986294}, {"id": 352324, "content": "独处是种艺术", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1680555}, {"id": 351560, "content": "我们并不孤单，只是总有自己的想法。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1652172}, {"id": 352588, "content": "只有点赞，没有评论", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1586458}, {"id": 351322, "content": "什么都不想干，莫名烦躁，有安排的任务，做的时候却充满了无力感。时常发呆，沉浸在自己的世界里，不愿被喊醒！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1560500}, {"id": 351585, "content": "可能会突然就很喜欢一个人，也会莫名就放弃了，并不再喜欢那个人…感觉总是变的很突然。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 380685}, {"id": 351342, "content": "看过了少妇白洁，也就能理解什么是孤独", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 832596}, {"id": 351125, "content": "刷到时间线不再更新内容，放下手机的那一刻倍感空虚", "image": null, "praise_count": 123, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 351126, "content": "曾经喜欢的号开始“变味”了，忍不住取关，网络上的关系实在是很难维系", "image": null, "praise_count": 72, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 351127, "content": "关注的好好的博主突然鸽了杳无音讯", "image": null, "praise_count": 19, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 351128, "content": "隔段时间翻看收藏列表，注销删除的一片荒芜", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 351130, "content": "开始演变出半括号式自说自话（并不", "image": null, "praise_count": 65, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 351131, "content": "因为想要终止孤独 而写下这段话 却感到更加孤独", "image": null, "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1572865}, {"id": 351132, "content": "来自凌晨两点零七分的孤独。", "image": null, "praise_count": 31, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1675727}, {"id": 351133, "content": "看着众人为“主流”的正义摇旗呐喊，自己不仅毫无波动甚至还感到丝丝寒意。", "image": null, "praise_count": 167, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1564241}, {"id": 352157, "content": "思虑过多", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1642571}, {"id": 351134, "content": "不停的翻着手机，却不知道要干什么，也没有消息", "image": null, "praise_count": 422, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1675282}, {"id": 351136, "content": "翻了很久，没有别的想联系的朋友，来来去去还是那几个人", "image": null, "praise_count": 94, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 930786}, {"id": 351137, "content": "一些孤独的爱好找到了同好和更多的资源 但现实中还是一个人孤独地喜欢", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 651076}, {"id": 351138, "content": "独木难支，愿好。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1428095}, {"id": 351139, "content": "不是一个人的时候就是孤独", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1440051}, {"id": 351140, "content": "其实孤独和独处是完全两个性质的。一定要活的有选择~希望大家都可以做到。", "image": null, "praise_count": 44, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1573962}, {"id": 351141, "content": "我听纯音乐的范围又扩大了", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1645855}, {"id": 352421, "content": "别人不懂我的想法，不懂我的快乐", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1684080}, {"id": 351142, "content": "人与人之间的连接变得轻而易举，人与人直接的离别也变得悄无声息", "image": null, "praise_count": 36, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1212252}, {"id": 351143, "content": "偶然看到世界另一个地方有和自己相似的人、经历、心情，那么即使现实中常常感到孤独，也有了些许慰藉", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1666475}, {"id": 351144, "content": "直播学习，直播读书，其实都是想找个伴儿。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1140981}, {"id": 351145, "content": "社交平台上的繁荣之下是各自深刻的孤独", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1594648}, {"id": 351146, "content": "人与人的沟通既方便又困难", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1552531}, {"id": 351147, "content": "我们总会露出善意的微笑🙂️，咦～我挺会笑的", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1646499}, {"id": 351148, "content": "不疼看相亲贴吧，思来想去，还是不敢网上发布个人信息", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1675761}, {"id": 351149, "content": "被微信为代表的现代通讯工具异化，单纯地成为信息单位反馈器，只是Input，出错时才Output", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 48994}, {"id": 351150, "content": "明明有床，却喜欢了谁窄窄的沙发", "image": "img/option/option/20191227111818jDmVTrM8x3XLCvNq.jpg", "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1169778}]}